story:
You are hiking in Snake Canyon when you find yourself lost in the strange, dimly lit Cave of Time. Gradually you can make out two passageways. One curves downward to the right; the other leads upward to the left. It occurs to you that the one leading down may go to the past and the one leading up may go to the future.

Which way will you choose?

Type '1' for the tunnel leading down
Type '2' for the tunnel leading up
